      "text": "命令层\n\n`src/cli.rs`\n- `generate-template(生成模板)`\n- `generate-schema(生成架构)`\n- `validate-config(验证配置)`\n- `completions(生成补全)`\n- `install-completions(安装补全)`\n- `uninstall-completions(卸载补全)`\n- `handle_config_command(处理配置命令)`",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "命令层\n\n`src/cli.rs`\n- `generate-template(生成模板)`\n- `generate-schema(生成架构)`\n- `validate-config(验证配置)`\n- `completions(生成补全)`\n- `install-completions(安装补全)`\n- `uninstall-completions(卸载补全)`\n- `handle_config_command(处理配置命令)`",
