      "updated": 1779248274482,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "运行时加载链路\n\n`src/config_load.rs`\n- `load_dotenv_for_path(加载环境文件)`\n- `load_layer_tree(加载配置层级树)`\n- 使用反向包含顺序合并文件\n- `merge_file_provider(合并文件提供器)`\n- 合并 `ConfiqueEnvProvider(环境变量提供器)`\n- `load_config_from_figment(从来源图提取配置)`\n- `trace_config_sources(跟踪配置来源)`\n\n对外函数\n- `load_config(加载配置)`\n- `build_config_figment(构建来源图)`\n- `load_config_with_figment(加载并返回来源图)`",
      "fontSize": 19.77504898343483,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "运行时加载链路\n\n`src/config_load.rs`\n- `load_dotenv_for_path(加载环境文件)`\n- `load_layer_tree(加载配置层级树)`\n- 使用反向包含顺序合并文件\n- `merge_file_provider(合并文件提供器)`\n- 合并 `ConfiqueEnvProvider(环境变量提供器)`\n- `load_config_from_figment(从来源图提取配置)`\n- `trace_config_sources(跟踪配置来源)`\n\n对外函数\n- `load_config(加载配置)`\n- `build_config_figment(构建来源图)`\n- `load_config_with_figment(加载并返回来源图)`",
